            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
                <div class="md:w-1/2">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-amber-800">Monthly Tiffin Service</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">Our flagship Tiffin Service provides busy professionals, students, and families with nutritious, homemade meals delivered daily. Subscribe monthly for hassle-free meal planning.</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                        <li>Daily fresh, home-cooked meals</li>
                        <li>Flexible subscription plans</li>
                        <li>Dietary preferences accommodated</li>
                        <li>Delivered by Mumbai's legendary Dabbawalas</li>
                        <li>Zero plastic packaging initiative</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
                    <div class="bg-amber-100 p-12 text-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto text-amber-600">
