                        </svg>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-amber-800 font-medium">Home Kitchen Marketplace</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-amber-800">Home Chef Marketplace</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">Our vibrant marketplace connects talented home chefs with customers seeking authentic, homemade food. From regional specialties to artisan pickles and preserves, discover unique culinary treasures.</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                        <li>Direct connection with home chefs</li>
                        <li>Regional specialties and local delicacies</li>
                        <li>Secure payment system</li>
                        <li>Quality assurance standards</li>
                        <li>Chef profiles and ratings</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Recipe Sharing -->
        <div class="mb-16">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
                <div class="md:w-1/2">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-amber-800">Recipe Sharing Community</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">Share your family recipes, cooking tips, and culinary secrets with our vibrant community. Preserve traditional recipes and discover new favorites from across India.</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                        <li>Upload and share family recipes</li>
                        <li>Discover recipes by region or category</li>
                        <li>Community voting and comments</li>
                        <li>Monthly featured recipes</li>
                        <li>Cooking tips and techniques</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
                    <div class="bg-amber-100 p-12 text-center">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto text-amber-600">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 7.5h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m-7.5 3h7.5m-7.5 3h7.5m3-9h3.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25M16.5 7.5V18a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25M16.5 7.5V4.875c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H4.125C3.504 3.75 3 4.254 3 4.875V18a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25h13.5M6 7.5h3v3H6v-3Z" />
