                        <p class="mt-4 text-amber-800 font-medium">Artisan Crafts</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-amber-800">Handmade Treasures</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">Beyond food, Zayka celebrates Indian handicrafts made by skilled artisans. From hand-embroidered textiles to traditional pottery, our platform showcases the rich artistic heritage of India.</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                        <li>Curated artisan products</li>
                        <li>Direct support to craftspeople</li>
                        <li>Traditional techniques and materials</li>
                        <li>Regional craft specialties</li>
                        <li>Artisan stories and heritage</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Why Choose Us -->
        <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-amber-100 p-8 mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-amber-800 text-center">Why Choose Zayka</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="text-center p-4">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto text-amber-600 mb-3">
