                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Empowering Homemakers</h3>
                    <p>Supporting women entrepreneurs to become financially independent through their culinary skills</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-4">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto text-amber-600 mb-3">
